<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title" style="padding:60px 20px; max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto;">
<h2 id="about-title" style="text-align:center;">About Task Masters</h2>
<p style="max-width:900px; margin:20px auto; font-size:1.1em; line-height:1.6; text-align:center;">
Task Masters is built on integrity, discipline, and a dedication to solving problems the right way—without shortcuts, without excuses.
Founded and operated by <strong>Cortez Bell</strong>, a hands-on professional with over 25 years of combined experience across building engineering, maintenance, project leadership, business operations, sales, and entrepreneurial management.
</p>g
<div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:30px; justify-content:center; margin-top:40px;">
    <div style="flex:1 1 300px; background:#f5f5f5; padding:25px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <h3 style="color:#6a0dad; text-align:center;">Mission</h3>
        <p style="line-height:1.6;">To provide honest, high‑quality, reliable building and business solutions that uplift clients, strengthen communities, and deliver results backed by skill, precision, and accountability.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1 1 300px; background:#f5f5f5; padding:25px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <h3 style="color:#6a0dad; text-align:center;">Values</h3>
        <ul style="line-height:1.6; padding-left:20px;">
            <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> Do the right thing whether someone is watching or not.</li>
            <li><strong>Accountability:</strong> Own every action, every outcome, every project.</li>
            <li><strong>Precision:</strong> Deliver work that’s clean, correct, and long‑lasting.</li>
            <li><strong>Community:</strong> Serve people, not just contracts.</li>
            <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Use modern solutions to solve old problems better.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1 1 300px; background:#f5f5f5; padding:25px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <h3 style="color:#6a0dad; text-align:center;">Who I Am</h3>
        <p style="line-height:1.6;">A builder. A problem solver. A strategist. A leader with experience across construction, repairs, electrical, plumbing, contracting, logistics, sales, risk management, and entrepreneurial operations. Every project receives the same energy: excellence.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</section>

